#. <section class="sutta" id="sn54.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn54.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Āsavakkhayasutta"
msgstr "20. The Ending of Defilements"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.341"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.20:1.1"
msgid "“… Āsavānaṃ khayāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is developed and "
"cultivated it leads to the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.2"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvito ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato "
"saṃyojanappahānāya saṃvattati …"
msgstr ""
"And how is immersion due to mindfulness of breathing developed and "
"cultivated so as to lead to giving up the fetters,"

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.3"
msgid "anusayasamugghātāya saṃvattati …"
msgstr "uprooting the underlying tendencies,"

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.4"
msgid "addhānapariññāya saṃvattati …"
msgstr "completely understanding the course of time,"

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.5"
msgid "āsavānaṃ khayāya saṃvattati?"
msgstr "and ending the defilements?"

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.6"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā … pe …"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant—gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or to "
"an empty hut—sits down cross-legged, with their body straight, and focuses "
"their mindfulness right there. …"

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.7"
msgid ""
"paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmīti sikkhati, paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmīti sikkhati."
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’"

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.8"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvito kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi evaṃ bahulīkato "
"saṃyojanappahānāya saṃvattati … pe …"
msgstr ""
"That’s how immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is developed and "
"cultivated so as to lead to giving up the fetters,"

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.9"
msgid "anusayasamugghātāya saṃvattati … pe …"
msgstr "uprooting the underlying tendencies,"

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.10"
msgid "addhānapariññāya saṃvattati … pe …"
msgstr "completely understanding the course of time,"

msgctxt "sn54.20:1.11"
msgid "āsavānaṃ khayāya saṃvattatī”ti."
msgstr "and ending the defilements.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.20:1.12"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.20:1.13"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.1"
msgid "Icchānaṅgalaṃ kaṅkheyyaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.2"
msgid "ānandā apare duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.3"
msgid "Bhikkhū saṃyojanānusayā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.4"
msgid "addhānaṃ āsavakkhayanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn54.20:2.5"
msgid "Ānāpānasaṃyuttaṃ dasamaṃ."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on Mindfulness of Breathing is the tenth section."
